Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,斯尼德公司向您奉上最诚挚的哀悼 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Sneed and Company offer their sincerest condolences, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.14,0:00:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,愿您坚强面对这般痛苦的时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}in this most trying hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.36,0:00:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,祖母她晚年还是很幸福的 斯尼德先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Grandmama had a good innings, Mr Sneed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,她曾如此充满活力\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She was so full of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我简直不敢相信她去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I can't believe she's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不是去了 雷德帕斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Not gone, Mr Redpath, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.70,0:00:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,睡着了而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Merely sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.78,0:00:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我能一个人静一静吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}May I have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.75,0:00:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.49,0:00:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在隔壁 您如有需要可以叫我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I shall be in the next, er, room should you require anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,又来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,住手\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,格温妮丝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Gwyneth!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快下来 又复活了一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Get down here now! We've got another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(600,600)\fn黑体\fs28\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\pos(189.538,171.6)}借尸还魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.05,0:02:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,按住那个 -我正按着呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Hold that one down! - I'm holding this one down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那就两个都按着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Well, hold them both down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我够不着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's not gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我承诺了给你时间旅行你就这么回报我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oi! I promised you a time machine and that's what you get.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你见识过了未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now you've seen the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们回过过去吧 1860年听起来如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}let's have a look at the past... 1860, How does 1860 sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.71,0:02:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,1860年怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What happened in 1860?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 一起去看看 抓住 要去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I don't know, let's find out! Hold on... here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.47,0:02:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,格温妮丝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Gwyneth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你死哪去了 丫头\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Where are you, girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,格温妮丝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Gwyneth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你哪去了 我喊了你半天了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Where've you been? I was shouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在马厩 先生 在为我们的马碎冰\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Been in the stable, sir, breaking the ice from Samson.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那你再回去 给它穿戴上马具\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Well, get back in there and harness him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要去干什么 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Whatever for, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,又有尸体活过来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The stiffs are getting lively again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,雷德帕斯先生的祖母 又起来活蹦乱跳了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Mr Redpath's grandmother, she's is up there on her feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.68,0:03:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不知所踪 我们得赶紧找到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and out there somewhere, on the streets, we've got to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,丢脸啊斯尼德先生 还要闹几次\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Mr Sneed, for shame, how many more times?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,简直天理难容啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's ungodly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,看我做什么 又不是我的错 赶紧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Don't look at me like it's MY fault. Now come on,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.76,0:03:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,快点去 她都86岁了 走不了太远的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}hurry up, she was 86, she can't have got far!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那雷德帕斯先生怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What about Mr Redpath?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你想好怎么处理他了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Did you deal with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,她已经把他"处理"了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}SHE did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,太糟了 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's awful, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我没资格说这话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I know it's not my place,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,所以请原谅我这般不懂规矩 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and please forgive me for talking out of turn, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但这事已经快不受控制了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but this is getting beyond now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这房子肯定遭了什么厄运\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Something terrible is happening in this house
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须得求助\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and we've got to get help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:03:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,当然得求助\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And we will,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但要先把那老太太抓回来锁住 别出事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}as soon as I've got that dead old woman locked up and safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,别再多嘴了 丫头\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now, stop prevaricating, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,备好灵车 我们这就收尸去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Get the hearse ready. We're going bodysnatching.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 -你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Blimey! - Telling me! You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得还好 没摔坏\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yeah, I think so. Nothing broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们到了吗 到哪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Did we make it? Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我成功了 真该给我颁块奖牌\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I did it! Give the man a medal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,地球那不勒斯 1860年12月24日\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Earth, Naples, December 24th, 1860.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,太诡异了 这是圣诞节啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's so weird. It's Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,请吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}All yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但就好像\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But it's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好好想想吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}think about it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,1860年的圣诞节仅有一次 就这一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Christmas 1860 happens once, just once, and then it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就永不再现 再也没有第二次了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}gone, it's finished, it'll never happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但对你例外\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Except for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:05:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以回到过去 重度那些已经逝去的时光\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You can go back and see days that are dead and gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,回到千万个日落之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}A hundred thousand sunsets ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,难怪你安定不下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No wonder you never stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这样活着挺好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Not a bad life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.63,0:05:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有人陪着更好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Better with two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那就去吧 -慢着慢着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Come on then! - Oi, oi, oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你干什么去 -去1860年啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Where d'you think you're going? - 1860.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你穿成这样出去会引发暴乱的 芭芭丽娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Go out there dressed like that, you'll start a riot, Barbarella.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那边有个衣柜\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There's a wardrobe through there,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,进左边第一个门 再右边第二个门\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}1st left, 2nd right,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,然后左边第三个门\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}third on the left,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.37,0:05:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,然后直走下楼梯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}go straight ahead, under the stairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,经过一堆箱子 左边第五个门 快去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}past the bins, fifth door on your left. Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.05,0:05:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,连个影子都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Not a sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,她哪去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.72,0:05:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,人间蒸发了呗 先生 还能哪去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She's vanished into the ether, sir. Where can she be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你来告诉我她去哪了 -您什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You tell me, girl. - What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,格温妮丝 你知道我什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Gwyneth, you know full well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能 先生 -快用你的天眼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No, sir, I can't. - Use the sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这样不好 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's not right, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧找到老太太 否则你就被开除了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Find the old lady or you're dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,用心去看 丫头\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Look inside, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,仔细看\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Look deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.54,0:06:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,她在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她迷路了 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She's lost, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.07,0:06:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她如此孤单\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She's so alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝啊 她头脑里有好多奇怪的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, my Lord. So many strange things in her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但她在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,她很兴奋\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She was excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,因为今晚的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}About tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,她去世之前 是想去见他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Before she passed on, she was going to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他是谁 -那个伟大的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Who's him? - The great man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,从伦敦一路而来 那个最最伟大的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}All the way from London, the great, great man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,狄更斯先生 狄更斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Mr Dickens? Mr Dickens?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了 狄更斯先生 该您上场了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Excuse me, sir, Mr Dickens, this is your call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,您还好吗 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Are you quite well, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 我很好 抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Splendid. Splendid. Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.34,0:06:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,您该上场了 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Time you were on, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是一个人闷一会儿而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I was just brooding...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是平安夜\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,本就不该独自一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Not the best of times to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,没人陪您来吗 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Did no-one travel with you, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人没来前排观赏吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No lady wife waiting out front?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,怕是没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,您若愿意 拙荆可以借您一用\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You can have mine if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不敢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, I wouldn't dare.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以来 在关于家庭事务方面\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I've, I've been rather... let's say, clumsy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以说是笨拙的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}with family matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地 我已老得采不动花草了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Thank God I'm too old to cause any more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,听您口气仿佛要退休了一般\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You speak as if it's all over, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.47,0:07:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能退休呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, it's never over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,一次又一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}On and on I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,重复同样的表演\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The same old show.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我就像个鬼魂\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm like a ghost,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,被诅咒永世重复经历这一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}condemned to repeat myself through all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,现在也不晚的 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's never too late, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,您还可以再想出一些新的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}you could always think up some new turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是我 也有想象力枯竭的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Even MY imagination grows stale.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我老了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm an old man,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:07:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,也许这辈子所有的想法都想完了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}perhaps I've thought everything I will ever think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不过万众瞩目的诱惑还是一如既往 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Still. The lure of the limelight's as potent as a pipe, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.65,0:08:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,闪亮登场\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}On with the motley.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哎哟喂 -不准笑我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Blimey. - Don't laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你看上去美极了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You look beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,考虑到…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Considering.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,考虑到什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Considering what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你是人类啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That you're human.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我就当做是夸奖好了 你不换衣服吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I think that's a compliment. Aren't you gonna change?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我换了衬衣 快来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I've changed my jumper! Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你不许动 上次就是你先\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You stay there, you've done this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这次该我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Ready for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,走进历史\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}History.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她就在里面 先生 我确信\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She's in there, sir, I'm certain of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:09:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,航线出了点问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I got the flight a bit wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,无所谓 -不是1860年 是1869年\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I don't care. - It's not 1860, it's 1869.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,无所谓 -而且也不是那不勒斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I don't care. - And it's not Naples.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我真不在乎 -是卡迪夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I don't care. - It's Cardiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这会儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now, it is a fact
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那个门环实实在在\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}that there was nothing particular at all
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,没有一点特殊的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}about the knocker on the door of this house
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,现在请随便哪一位 要是可以的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but let any man explain to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,给我解释一下 那是怎么发生的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}if he can, how it happened that Scrooge,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,斯克鲁奇把他的钥匙插进门锁以后\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}having his key in the lock of the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,看到那个门环\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}saw in the knocker,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没有经过任何中间的变化过程\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}without its undergoing any intermediate process of change,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,却已不再是门环 而是马莱的脸\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}not a knocker, but Marley's face!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,马莱的脸哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Marley's face!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,它看着斯克鲁奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It looked at Scrooge
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,眼神像往常一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}as Marley used to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就像\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It looked like...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.87,0:11:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, my Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就像 就像她一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}it looked... like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么戏法\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What phantasmagoria is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这还差不多\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's more like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,请诸位坐回座位上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Stay in your seats, I, I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是彩灯戏法而已 是假的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It is a lantern show, trickery!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她在那儿 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There she is, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我看见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I can see that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,全世界都看见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Whole bloomin' world can see that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,妙极了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你看见那东西从哪来的了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Did you see where it came from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看哪 幕后主使现身了 是不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Ah! The wag reveals himself, does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这下你满意了吧 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I trust you're satisfied, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.46,0:12:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你们 放开她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oi! Leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,博士 我去追他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Doctor! I'll get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.57,0:12:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,小心\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.09,0:12:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,它说什么了吗 会说话吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Did it say anything? Can it speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便说一下 我是博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm the Doctor, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,博士 你看起来像个苦工\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Doctor? You look more like a navvy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这衬衫有什么问题吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What's wrong with this jumper?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,真不幸啊 小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}A tragedy, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不劳您忧心 交由我和主人应付即可\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Don't worry yourself, me and the master'll deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,其实这位可怜的夫人得了脑膜炎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Fact is, this poor lady's been taken with a brain-fever
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须要将她送去医院\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and we have to get her to the infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,她都凉了 她死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She's cold. She's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天呐 你们对她做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, my God, what did you do to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What did you do that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,她知道的太多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She's seen too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,把她抬进灵车里 去抬腿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Get her in the hearse! Legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,煤气\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那东西是煤气构成的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's made of gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,洛斯 -你休想跑 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Rose! - You're not escaping me, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你对那鬼怪了解多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What do you know about that hob-goblin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我估计是使用玻璃投影 谁指使你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Projection on glass, I suppose. Who put you up to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计 现在没空 多谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yeah, mate, not now, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你 跟着那辆灵车\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oi! You! Follow that hearse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 我做不到 -为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Can't do that, sir. - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 我来告诉你为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Why not? I'll give you a very good reason why not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这是我的马车\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Because this is my coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那就快上车啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Well, get in, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,走\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 你快跟丢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Come on, you're losing them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.90,0:13:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,您没事吧 狄更斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Everything in order, Mr. Dickens?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会没事 -他叫你什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No, it is not! - What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我先说 我并不是没有幽默感…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Let me say this first. I am not without a sense of humour...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,狄更斯 -是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Dickens? -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.14,0:14:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,查尔斯·狄更斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Charles Dickens?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,对 -鼎鼎大名的查尔斯·狄更斯吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}-Yes! -THE Charles Dickens?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,需要我赶走他吗 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Should I remove the gentleman, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,查尔斯·狄更斯 你真是才华横溢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Charles Dickens,You're brilliant, you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,彻彻底底的天才啊 你的书我都读过\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Completely, 100% brilliant! I've read 'em all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,《远大前程》《雾都孤儿》\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Great Expectations, Oliver Twist,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那部讲鬼魂的叫什么来着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and what's the other one, the one with the ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,《圣诞颂歌》吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Christmas Carol?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不 是和火车有关的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No, no, no, the one with the trains.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,《信号员》没错就是它 特别恐怖\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The Signalman, that's it, terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,史上最棒的短篇小说\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The best short story ever written!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是个天才\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You're a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,需要我赶走他吗 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Do you want me to get rid of him, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不必 让他待在这吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Er, no, I think he can stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.03,0:14:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,说真的 查尔斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Honestly, Charles... er,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.95,0:14:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我能直呼你名吗 我是你的忠实粉丝啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}can I call you Charles? I'm such a big fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么 忠实什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Eh, you're a what? A big what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,粉丝 头号粉丝就是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Fan. Number one fan, that's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么会是"风扇"呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How exactly are you a "fan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你哪里像那个给人带来凉爽的东西啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}In what way do you resemble a means of keeping oneself cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,粉丝是指狂热者 崇拜你 痴迷于你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No, it means fanatic. Give over to you, mind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,话说《马丁·索威特》里面那个美国人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}For God's sake, that American bit in Martin Chuzzlewit,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.49,0:14:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}what's that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,只是纯粹为了凑字数吗 太糟糕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Was that just padding or what? It's rubbish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是说是我的粉丝吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I thought you were my fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 要是你没法接受批评\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, well, if you can't take criticism...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,继续写出像《老古玩店》那样的结局吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Go on, do the death of Little Nell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那真是太感人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It cracks me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 不聊这些了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No! Sorry! Forget about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 再快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Come on! Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来 到底谁在那辆灵车里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}By the way, who exactly is in that hearse?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我朋友 她才19岁 都是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}My friend. She's only 19 and it's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我本该照顾好她 现在却让她遇到危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She's in my care, now she's in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那干嘛还要浪费时间谈那些老掉牙的小说\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Why are we wasting my time talking about dry old books?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这件事重要得多呢 车夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This is much more important. Driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,动作快点 追上去 -遵命 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Be swift! The chase is on! - Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 查理 -从来没人这么叫\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Attaboy, Charlie. - Nobody calls me Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.90,0:15:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,女人们都这么叫你 -你怎么知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The ladies do. - How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.82,0:15:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我早说过了 我可是头号…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I told you! I'm your number one...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,头号粉丝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Number one fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这位可怜的女孩还活着呢 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The poor girl's still alive, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,您打算怎么处理她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}what are we going to do with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来没打算这么做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I didn't plan any of this, did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,死人莫名复活难道还是我的错吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Is it my fault if the dead won't stay dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那是谁的错 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Then whose fault is it, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这种事总发生在我们身上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Why is this happening to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.48,0:15:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前帮过主教一个忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I did the Bishop a favour once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,把他侄子化装成天使模样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Made his nephew look like a cherub
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他侄子可是在河浜里死了两个礼拜\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}even though he'd been a fortnight in the weir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:16:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定他能优惠点为我们驱邪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Hey, perhaps he'll do us an exorcism on the cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.01,0:16:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,说我不在 告诉他们店已打烊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Say I'm not in. Tell 'em we're closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,就…让他们走开就行\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Just, just, get rid of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们抱歉 本店已打烊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm sorry sir, we're closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.95,0:16:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,乱说 什么时候殡仪馆也正常上下班了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Nonsense, since when did an undertaker keep office hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,随时都会有人死亡 我要求见你们老板\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The dead don't die on schedule, I demand to see your master.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他不在 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He's not in, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,别骗我 孩子 把老板叫来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Don't lie to me, child, summon the master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 狄更斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm awfully sorry, Mr Dickens,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但老板现在身体不适\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but the master is indisposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你们家煤气出故障了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Having trouble with your gas?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,到底在搞什么鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What the Shakespeare is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:16:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你在恶作剧吧 只是恶作剧吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You're kidding me, yeah? You're just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,只是在逗我玩吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You are kidding me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 不是恶作剧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}OK, not kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,先生您不能进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You're not allowed inside, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.85,0:17:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,墙里面有动静\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There's something inside the walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,煤气管道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The gas pipes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,某种东西住在煤气里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Something's living inside the gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,放我出去 快开门\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Let me out! Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是她 -救命啊 放我出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's her! - Please, let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你们怎么就这么闯进来 这可是我家\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How dare you, sir! This is my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么跟你说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,放我出去 谁来开下门啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Let me out, somebody open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,开门啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.50,0:17:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我的舞伴\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I think this is my dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,恶作剧吧 我们一定是被催眠了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's a prank. Must be. We're under some mesmeric influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没被催眠 是尸体复活了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No, we are not, the dead are walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 -你好 你朋友叫什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Hi. - Hi. Who's your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.59,0:18:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,查尔斯·狄更斯 -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Charles Dickens. - OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我是博士 你们是谁 想要干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}My name's the Doctor. Who are you, then? What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,失败 打开裂缝 我们要死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Failing! Open the rift. We're dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,被困于此形态\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Trapped in this form.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,无法继续维持 救救我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Cannot sustain. Help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.25,0:18:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,先是给我下迷药 然后还绑架我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}First you drug me, then you kidnap me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,别以为我不知道你的手在乱摸\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and don't think I didn't feel your hands having a quick wander,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你个老色鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}you dirty old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不许这样跟我说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I won't be spoken to like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.92,0:18:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,还把我关进满是僵尸的房间里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Then you sent me in a room full of zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.67,0:18:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这还不够\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And if that ain't enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你居然跑了 留我一个人等死\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}you swan off and leave me to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,说话呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}So come on! Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是我的错 是这房子的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's not my fault, it's this house!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这房子很早就有传闻\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It always had a reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:18:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,闹鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Haunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.58,0:18:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但我从不把它当回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But I never had much bother,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.71,0:19:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,直到大概三个月前 那些死人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}until about three months back. And then the stiffs...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那些…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The, erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那些离世者开始变得不安宁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}the dear departed started getting restless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,荒唐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Tommyrot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你也看到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You witnessed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,根本控制不住啊 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Can't keep the beggars down, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会走\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,最奇怪的是 虽然他们复活了…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And it's the queerest thing, but they hang onto scraps...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,按您要求加了两块糖 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Two sugars, sir, just how you like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,一个曾经是教堂司事的老头\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}One old fella, used to be a sexton,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,差点就走进了他自己的追悼会现场\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}almost walked into his own memorial service.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,就像那位老太太\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Just like the old lady,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,按照她的生前计划去看先生您的演出\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}going to your performance, sir, just as she'd planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,荒谬至极\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Morbid fancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,查尔斯 你当时也在场\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, Charles, you were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到的只是幻象\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I saw nothing but an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想否认 就别浪费我的时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}If you're going to deny it, don't waste my time,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}just shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.27,0:19:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那些气体怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What about the gas?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那是最近出现的 以前从没看到过\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's new, sir. I never seen anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,说明它越来越强 裂缝越来越大\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Means it's getting stronger. The rift's getting wider,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有东西在穿过裂缝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and something's sneaking through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.39,0:19:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,裂缝是什么 -时间和空间的脆弱点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What's the rift? - A weak point in time and space.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:19:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,两个世界的连接处\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}A connection between this place and another.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.95,0:19:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,大多数鬼故事都是这个造成的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's the cause of ghost stories, most of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这房子才买得这么便宜\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's how I got the house so cheap,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼故事代代相传\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}stories going back generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗中的回声 空中的奇怪歌声\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Echoes in the dark. Queer songs in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.38,0:20:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,阴影般的感受\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And this feeling, like a shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,掠过心头\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}passing over your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不介意说实话 这对做生意挺有好处\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Mind you, truth be told, it's been good for business,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.58,0:20:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,人们对我们这种阴森森的行当的想法也是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}just what people expect from a gloomy old trade like mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.61,0:20:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.71,0:20:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在找绳子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Checking for strings?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.32,0:20:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,或者金属丝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Wires... perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:21:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定有什么机械装置才整出这诡计\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There must be some mechanism behind this fraud.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样 查尔斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, come on, Charles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我不该叫你闭嘴 我道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}All right, I shouldn't have told you to shut up. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但你算是拥有全世界顶尖聪明的脑袋\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But you've got one of the best minds in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你也看到那些气体怪物了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and you saw those gas creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.34,0:21:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法接受\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I cannot accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,当人类尸体在腐烂时会怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And what does the human body do, when it decomposes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,会分解产生气体\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It breaks down. Produces gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这很适合那些气体怪物\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Perfect home for these gas-things,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就像借助交通工具般借助尸气溜进来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}they can slip inside, use it as a vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你的车夫和马车 -别说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Just like your driver and his coach.- Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.46,0:21:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,难道我对这个世界的认识全部错了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Can it be that I have the world entirely wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.04,0:21:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不是错 只是还有许多有待学习\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Not wrong. There's just more to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.59,0:21:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直批判那些幻想家\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I've always railed against the fantasists!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我和所有人一样爱幻象并痴迷于此\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, I loved an illusion as much as the next man, reveled in them,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但幻象就只是幻象\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but that's exactly what they were, illusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,和真实世界是不一样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The real world is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.98,0:21:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我一生致力于消除不公正对待\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I dedicated myself to that-- injustices,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.44,0:21:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这个伟大的社会目标\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}the great social causes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望我的贡献是有用的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I hoped that I was a force for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:21:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,可你现在告诉我真实世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now, you tell me that the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:22:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,却是幽灵和南瓜灯的地盘\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}is a realm of spectres and Jack o'lanterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.54,0:22:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}In which case...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.30,0:22:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我是否虚度了这短暂人生 博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}have I wasted my brief span here, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.38,0:22:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我的生命是否毫无价值\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Has it all been for nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.80,0:22:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,小姐 你不该来帮忙的 这不合礼节\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Please, miss, you shouldn't be helping, it's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.04,0:22:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,别说笑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Don't be daft,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我打赌斯尼德让你干的活一定多得累死人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I bet Sneed works you to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.18,0:22:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你的工钱多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How much do you get paid?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.86,0:22:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,一年八英镑 小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Eight pound a year, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.65,0:22:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.47,0:22:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 但我能有六英镑就知足了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I know! I would've been happy with six.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.68,0:22:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那你上过学吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}So did you even go to school, or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.74,0:22:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 你以为我是文盲吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Of course I did, what do you think I am, an urchin?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.49,0:22:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我每周日都准时去上课\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I went every Sunday, nice and proper.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.11,0:22:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 一周一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What, once a week?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.57,0:22:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,学数学还有其他内容\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We did sums and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.48,0:22:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}To be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.04,0:22:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我特别讨厌上学 -我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I hated every second. - Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.97,0:23:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,别告诉其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Don't tell anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.53,0:23:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,有一周我没去上课 一个人跑去荒地玩\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but one week I didn't go and I ran down the Heath, all on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.30,0:23:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事我干得多呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I did plenty of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.84,0:23:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前经常和我同学席琳溜出去逛商店\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I used to go round the shops with my mate, Shareen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.95,0:23:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还经常跑去看男孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And we used to go and look at boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.97,0:23:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这个我就不清楚了 小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Well, I don't know much about that, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.57,0:23:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 时代不会相差这么多吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, come on, times haven't changed that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.32,0:23:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我打赌你也干过 -我没有 小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I bet you've done the same. - I don't think so, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.87,0:23:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,格温妮丝 你可以告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Gwyneth, you can tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.84,0:23:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜你肯定有心上人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I bet you've got your eye on someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.14,0:23:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我想 确实有这么一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I suppose, there is one lad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.34,0:23:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,屠夫家的孩子 每周二过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The butcher's boy, he comes by every Tuesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.28,0:23:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他的笑容特别可爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Such a lovely smile on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.80,0:23:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢可爱的笑容\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I like a nice smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.52,0:23:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,可爱的微笑 迷人的翘臀\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Good smile, nice bum.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.27,0:23:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒是第一次听说这种说法\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Well, I have never heard the like!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.09,0:23:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,约他出来 喝杯茶什么的 这是开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Ask him out. Give him a cup of tea or something, that's a start.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.17,0:23:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我发誓这是我见过最奇怪的事了 小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I swear, it's the strangest thing, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.51,0:24:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你穿着得体还如此有教养\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You've got all the clothes and the breeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.68,0:24:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但是说的话却这么疯狂\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But you talk like some sort of wild thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.08,0:24:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我就是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Maybe I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.03,0:24:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定这是好事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Maybe that's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.54,0:24:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你的人生不能只局限在斯尼德先生这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You need a bit more in your life than Mr Sneed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.62,0:24:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不该这样说\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, no, that's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.12,0:24:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,老斯尼德也没有那么坏\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He's not so bad, old Sneed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.05,0:24:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他很好心地收留了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He was very kind to me to take me in,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.40,0:24:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我12岁时我的父母死于流感\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}cos I lost my mum and dad to the flu when I was 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.03,0:24:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.59,0:24:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢您 小姐 不过我们总会团聚的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Thank you, Miss. But I'll be with them again, one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.43,0:24:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,和他们在天堂里重逢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}sitting with them in Paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.27,0:24:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我幸运的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I shall be so blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.76,0:24:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他们一定在天上等我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They're waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.88,0:24:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定您父亲也在天上等着您呢 小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Maybe your dad's up there waiting for you too, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.85,0:24:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.13,0:24:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,谁告诉你我爸爸已经过世了的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Um, who told you he was dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.84,0:24:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道 应该是博士说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I dunno, must've been the Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.00,0:24:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲几年前就死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}My father died years back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.70,0:24:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但您最近都在想他 比以往更想\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You've been thinking about him lately. More than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.89,0:25:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,应该吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.77,0:25:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How do you know all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.59,0:25:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,斯尼德说我想得太多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Mr. Sneed says I think too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.13,0:25:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我老是一个人在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm all alone down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.30,0:25:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我打赌您肯定有好多佣人 对不对小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I bet you've got dozens of servants, haven't you, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.63,0:25:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我在的地方可没有佣人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No, no servants where I'm from.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.28,0:25:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,您从那么远的地方过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And you've come such a long way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.45,0:25:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么这么认为\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What makes you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.76,0:25:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你是从伦敦来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You're from London.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.50,0:25:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我在画上看过伦敦的样子 但你的不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I've seen London in drawings, but never like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.67,0:25:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,人们都行色匆匆\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}all those people rushing about.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.75,0:25:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,还有半裸的 简直不知廉耻\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Half-naked, for shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.56,0:25:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,还有那些噪音\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And the noise...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.94,0:25:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,还有跑来跑去的金属盒子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and the metal boxes racing past...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.25,0:25:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,还有飞在空中的鸟\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and the birds in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.96,0:25:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不 鸟也是金属做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No, no, they're metal as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.14,0:25:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,金属鸟里都是人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Metal birds with people in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.53,0:25:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,人在天上飞\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}People are flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.59,0:25:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,而你 你飞得那么远\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And you. You've flown so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.06,0:25:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,比谁都远\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Further than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.67,0:26:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你见到的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The things you've seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.65,0:26:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那些黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.36,0:26:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,大恶狼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The big Bad Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.24,0:26:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起 小姐 -没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm sorry. I'm sorry, Miss. - It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.17,0:26:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我控制不住 我从小就这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I can't help it. Ever since I was a little girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.38,0:26:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈妈说我有特殊的视力\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}my mum said I had the sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.57,0:26:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,她叫我把这种能力隐藏起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She told me to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.57,0:26:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在这种能力越来越强大了 是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But it's getting stronger. More powerful. Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.82,0:26:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一直在增长 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}All the time, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.78,0:26:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,每天晚上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Every night,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.30,0:26:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我都会听到脑海中有人说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}voices in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.15,0:26:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你在那个裂口边上长大\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You grew up on top of the rift.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.87,0:26:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你是它的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You're part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.86,0:26:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是钥匙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You're the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.82,0:26:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想弄清楚是怎么回事 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I've tried to make sense of it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.75,0:26:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,咨询过\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Consulted with...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.49,0:26:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,各种各样的灵媒 巫师\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}spiritualists, table-rappers, all sorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.57,0:26:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这应该有点帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Well, that should help.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.28,0:26:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你能教我们该怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You can show us what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.62,0:26:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,什么怎么办 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What to do where, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.22,0:26:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们准备来一场降神会\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We're going to have a seance.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.70,0:26:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,莫罗克太太在布特镇时\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This is how Madame Mortlock summons
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.67,0:26:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这么召唤出迷雾之都的幽灵的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}those from the Land of Mists, down in Butetown.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.57,0:27:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 我们得把手拉起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Come. We must all join hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.92,0:27:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会参与这种事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I can't take part in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.25,0:27:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,反悔了吗 来吧 思想放开点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Humbug? Come on. Open mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.19,0:27:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是专门揭穿这种廉价把戏的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This is precisely the sort of cheap mummery I strive to unmask.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.04,0:27:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,降神会\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Seances!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.59,0:27:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不就是用几面闪闪的鼓\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Nothing but luminous tambourines
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.55,0:27:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,和藏在膝盖间的小风琴故弄玄虚吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and a squeeze-box concealed between the knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.14,0:27:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这姑娘什么都不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This girl knows nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.51,0:27:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,现在先别急着反对\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now, don't antagonise her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.13,0:27:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我更喜欢看到一个快乐的灵媒\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I love a happy medium.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.96,0:27:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信你能说出这种话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I can't believe you just said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.24,0:27:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 我们说不定需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Come on. We might need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.22,0:27:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.81,0:27:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,格温妮丝 来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now, Gwyneth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.64,0:27:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,召唤吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Reach out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.08,0:27:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,和我们说话吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Speak to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.11,0:27:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你在么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.07,0:27:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,降临吧 幽灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Spirits, come.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.27,0:27:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,向我们倾诉 让我们减轻你的负担\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Speak to us that we may relieve your burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.58,0:27:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你听到了没\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Can you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.50,0:27:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都不会发生的 这太愚蠢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Nothing can happen, this is sheer folly.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.99,0:28:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,快看她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.17,0:28:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到它们了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.11,0:28:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉到它们了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I feel them!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.52,0:28:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,它在说什么 -它没法通过裂口\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What's it saying? - It can't get through the rift.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.65,0:28:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,格温妮丝 不是它在控制你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Gwyneth, it's not controlling you,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.99,0:28:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,而是你在控制它\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}you're controlling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.08,0:28:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,现在注视着它们 让它们通过\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now look deep. Allow them through.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.28,0:28:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.96,0:28:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以的 相信自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yes, you can. Just believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.75,0:28:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我对你有信心 格温妮丝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I have faith in you, Gwyneth.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.66,0:28:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,和它们联结起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Make the link.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.02,0:28:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.88,0:28:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Great God!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.94,0:28:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,另一个世界的幽灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Spirits from the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.56,0:28:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是宇宙的另一端\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The other side of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.08,0:28:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,可怜可怜我们吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Pity us!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.15,0:28:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,可怜可怜格尔斯吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Pity the Gelth!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.81,0:28:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,时间所剩不多 帮帮我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There is so little time. Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.93,0:28:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你要我们怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What do you want us to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.15,0:29:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,裂口 把这个女孩带到裂口那去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The rift. Take the girl to the rift.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.34,0:29:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,建立连接\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Make the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.41,0:29:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.66,0:29:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经所剩不多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We are so very few.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.28,0:29:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最后的族人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The last of our kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.90,0:29:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们面临着灭亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We face extinction!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.26,0:29:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 发生什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Why, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.00,0:29:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也曾有过肉体 和你们一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Once we had a physical form, like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.21,0:29:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但是战争来临了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But then the War came.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.64,0:29:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,什么战争 -时间大战\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}War? What war? - The Time War.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.71,0:29:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,整个宇宙发生了剧变\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The whole universe convulsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.74,0:29:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,时间大战对于低等种族来说毫无影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The Time War raged, invisible to smaller species
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.33,0:29:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但是对于高级种族来说却是毁灭性的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but devastating to higher forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.47,0:29:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的躯体都毁灭了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Our bodies wasted away.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.31,0:29:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只能以气体的形式存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We're trapped in this gaseous state.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.84,0:29:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你们才需要这些尸体\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}So that's why you need the corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.96,0:29:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想挺直身板\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We want to stand tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.26,0:29:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,感受阳光的温度\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}To feel the sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.17,0:29:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,再次感受生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}To live again.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.31,0:29:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要肉体 而你们却在丢弃尸体\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We need a physical form and your dead are abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.52,0:29:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,它们都被浪费了 给我们吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They go to waste. Give them to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.90,0:29:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,可是不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But we can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.21,0:29:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.95,0:29:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这不… 我是说这不\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's not... I mean,it's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.10,0:30:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不体面还是不礼貌 这样能救它们的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Not decent? Not polite? It could save their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.15,0:30:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,打开裂口吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Open the rift.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.55,0:30:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,让格尔斯过来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Let the Gelth through.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.79,0:30:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在消逝 救救我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We're dying. Help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.57,0:30:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,可怜可怜格尔斯吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Pity the Gelth!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.67,0:30:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,格温妮丝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Gwyneth!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.10,0:30:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,都是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}All true.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.41,0:30:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's all true.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.17,0:30:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 你躺着就行\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's all right. You just sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.92,0:30:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但我的天使呢 小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But my angels, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.01,0:30:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,它们来了 是吗 它们需要我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They came, didn't they? They need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.67,0:30:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,它们的确需要你 格温妮丝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They do need you, Gwyneth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.93,0:30:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你是它们存活的唯一机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You're their only chance of survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.56,0:30:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你说过了 别来烦她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I told you, leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.24,0:30:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,她累坏了 你的战争也不该她来打\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She's exhausted and she's not fighting your battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.82,0:30:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,来把这个喝了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now, drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.23,0:30:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么 博士 再解释一遍\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But what did you say, Doctor? Explain it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.89,0:30:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,它们是什么 -外星人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What are they? - Aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.32,0:31:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说 就像外国人一样吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Like, foreigners, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.31,0:31:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,非常远的外国 从上面来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Pretty foreign, yeah. From up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.59,0:31:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,布雷肯吗 -差不多\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Brecon? - Close.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.15,0:31:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,它们想从布雷肯去卡迪夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And they've been trying to get through from Brecon to Cardiff
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.18,0:31:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但是路堵住了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but the road's blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.51,0:31:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一部分人可以通过\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Only a few can get through.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.61,0:31:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅如此 它们还很虚弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Even then, they're weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.34,0:31:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,它们只能控制那些躯体一小段时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They can only test-drive the bodies for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.64,0:31:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就得转回气体形态 躲回管道里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Then they have to revert to gas and hide in the pipes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.35,0:31:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以它们才需要那个女孩吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Which is why they need the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.07,0:31:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不能把她给它们 -但她能帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They're not having her. - But she can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.06,0:31:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,她成为了那个裂口的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Living on the rift she's become part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.52,0:31:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,她能打开裂口 建立连接让他们通过\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She can open it up, make a bridge and let them through.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.89,0:31:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,难以置信 幽灵其实不是鬼魂\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Incredible. Ghosts that are not ghosts
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.02,0:31:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,而是从另一个世界来的生灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but beings from another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.32,0:31:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,只能靠寄生在尸体上才能活在我们的世界里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Who can only exist in our realm by inhabiting cadavers.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.17,0:31:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这套办法挺不错 说不定能行\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Good system. It might work.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.69,0:31:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能让它们寄生在死人身体里乱跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You can't let them run around inside of dead people!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.14,0:31:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不行 就跟循环利用一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Why not? It's like recycling.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.88,0:31:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,说真的 不行 -说真的 可以\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Seriously though, you can't. - Seriously though, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.63,0:31:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,可这样做就是不对\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But it's just wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.74,0:31:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那些尸体都曾是活生生的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Those bodies were living people.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.44,0:31:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就算死了我们也应该尊重他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We should respect them, even in death.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.58,0:31:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你带着捐献同意书吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Do you carry a donor card?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.35,0:31:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这不一样 这 -本来就不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's different, that's... - It is different, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.91,0:31:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我这里道德标准不一样 要么适应 要么回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's a different morality. Get used to it. Or go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.02,0:32:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你也听到了 它们说时间不多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You heard what they said, time's short.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.99,0:32:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,最后几个格尔斯快死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I can't worry about a few corpses
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.50,0:32:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我没空来管几具尸体的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}when the last of the Gelth could be dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.44,0:32:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我不管 它们不能利用她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I don't care, they're not using her.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.34,0:32:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我能说句话吗 小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Don't I get a say, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.76,0:32:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,可以 哦不\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Well, yes... no.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.22,0:32:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你不明白发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You don't understand what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.20,0:32:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,小姐 你会这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You would say that, Miss,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.94,0:32:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为你已经在脑子里下了定论\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}cos that's very clear inside your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.12,0:32:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我很笨\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That you think I'm stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.45,0:32:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这样的 -但事实如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That's not fair. - It's true though.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.27,0:32:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,可能你来的地方 事情完全不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Things might be very different where you're from,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.04,0:32:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但此时此刻 我知道我在想什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}but here and now, I know my own mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.49,0:32:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天使们需要我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And the angels need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.08,0:32:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,博士 我应该干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Doctor? What do I have to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.60,0:32:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么都不用干\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You don't have to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.34,0:32:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,小时候它们就一直对着我唱歌\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They've been singing to me since I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.21,0:32:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得它们是我妈妈派来照顾我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Sent by my mum on holy mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.64,0:32:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我该怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}so tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.16,0:32:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得找到裂口\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We need to find the rift.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.73,0:32:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这房子就建在一个薄弱点上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This house is on a weak-spot,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.07,0:32:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,所以肯定有个地方的束缚是最弱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}so there must be a spot that's weaker than any other.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.01,0:32:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,斯尼德先生 这房子最弱的地方在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Mr Sneed, what's the weakest part of this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.28,0:32:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,幽灵最多的地方在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The place where most of the ghosts have been seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.25,0:33:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那肯定是停尸房了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}That would be the morgue.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.81,0:33:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,估计你也不会说露台之类的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}No chance you were going to say gazebo, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.36,0:33:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这才是真正的"荒凉山庄"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Talk about bleak house.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.58,0:33:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,事实是 博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The thing is, Doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.01,0:33:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,格尔斯不会成功 因为我知道他们没有成功\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}the Gelth don't succeed, cos I know they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.78,0:33:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道1869年尸体没有满大街跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I know for a fact that corpses weren't walking round in 1869.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.34,0:33:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,时间是不断变化的 每一秒都在改变\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Time's in flux, changing every second.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.25,0:33:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你那舒适的小天地很有可能就此改写\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Your cosy little world could be rewritten like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.39,0:33:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没有绝对安全的事 记住 根本没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Nothing is safe. Remember that. Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.77,0:33:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,博士 我觉得这房间越来越冷了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Doctor, I think the room is getting colder.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.51,0:33:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他们来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.22,0:33:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你们来帮我们了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You've come to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.21,0:33:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,赞美博士 赞美他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Praise the Doctor! Praise him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.43,0:33:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要保证不会伤害她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Promise you won't hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.82,0:33:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 求你了 时间不多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Hurry! Please! So little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.81,0:33:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,可怜可怜格尔斯吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Pity the Gelth!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.61,0:33:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你们过来之后我会带你们去别的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'll take you somewhere else after the transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.17,0:34:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,去一个你们能拥有正常身体的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Somewhere you can build proper bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.79,0:34:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是暂时的解决办法 明白吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This isn't a permanent solution, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.01,0:34:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天使们 我能帮他们活下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}My angels! I can help them live.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.72,0:34:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,薄弱点在哪里 -这里 拱门下方\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}OK, where's the weak point? - Here, beneath the arch!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.63,0:34:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,拱门下方\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Beneath the arch.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.99,0:34:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你没必要这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You don't have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.27,0:34:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天使们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}My angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.36,0:34:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,建立连接\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Establish the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.47,0:34:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,连接虚空 让我们通过吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Reach out to the void. Let us through!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.87,0:34:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.44,0:34:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我能看见你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I can see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.55,0:34:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我能看见你们 来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I can see you! Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.42,0:34:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,连接正在建立\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Bridgehead establishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.97,0:34:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,到我这里来 到这个世界来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Come to me. Come to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.80,0:34:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,可怜的迷路的灵魂\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Poor lost souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.80,0:34:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,开始了 连接建立完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It has begun! The bridge is made.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.30,0:34:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,她献身给了格尔斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She has given herself to the Gelth!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.69,0:34:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,数量挺多啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Rather a lot of them, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.48,0:34:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,连接通畅 我们来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The bridge is open. We descend.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.90,0:34:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,格尔斯将强行通过\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The Gelth will come through in force.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.77,0:34:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你说过你们为数不多\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You said that you were few in number!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.44,0:35:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,几十亿而已 我们都需要尸体\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}A few billion! And all of us in need of corpses!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.28,0:35:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,格温妮丝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now, Gwyneth,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.91,0:35:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,停下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.38,0:35:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,听主人的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Listen to your master!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.96,0:35:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这已经过分了 别闹了 孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This has gone far enough, stop dabbling,child,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.40,0:35:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,别管他们了 我求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and leave these things alone, I beg of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.80,0:35:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,斯尼德先生 快回来 -别靠近\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Mr Sneed, get back! - Don't go near.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.01,0:35:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我开始觉得有点不对劲了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I think it's going a little bit wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.14,0:35:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我加入了格尔斯军团\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I have joined the legions of the Gelth.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.68,0:35:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 和我们一起进军 -天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Come, march with us. - Oh, glory!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.23,0:35:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要躯体 你们所有人 必死\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We need bodies. All of you, dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.35,0:35:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,全人类 必死\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The human race, dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.15,0:35:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,格温妮丝 阻止他们 送他们回去 快\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Gwyneth, stop them! Send them back, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.57,0:36:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,又有三具躯体 占有它们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Three more bodies! Convert them!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.33,0:36:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,把它们变成承载格尔斯之肉身\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Make them vessels for the Gelth!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.38,0:36:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,博士 我无法陪伴你们了 抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Doctor, I can't! I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.42,0:36:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你们带来的新世界 我无法接受\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This new world of yours, it's too much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.73,0:36:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我实在\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm so...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.70,0:36:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,献身荣耀吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Give yourself to glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.81,0:36:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,将你们的生命献给格尔斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Sacrifice your lives to the Gelth.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.38,0:36:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我还相信了你们 同情了你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I trusted you. I pitied you!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.09,0:36:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不需要你的同情\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We don't want your pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.78,0:36:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要这个世界和其中所有躯体\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We want this world and all its flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.96,0:36:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我还活着你们就休想\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Not while I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.38,0:36:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那就去死吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Then live no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.59,0:36:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我不能死 告诉我我不会死\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But I can't die. Tell me I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.69,0:36:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这个年代我都还没出生 我怎么可能死呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I haven't even been born yet, it's impossible for me to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.75,0:36:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,对不对\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.10,0:37:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.08,0:37:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好难受 这种气体对我们有害\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Failing! Atmosphere hostile!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.59,0:37:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,煤气\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.41,0:37:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是煤气\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.25,0:37:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这是1869年 我怎么能死在这一年\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But it's 1869, how can I die now?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.71,0:37:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,时间不是直线 可能被扭曲成任何形状\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Time isn't a straight line, it can twist into any shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.26,0:37:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以在二十世纪出生 在十九世纪死去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You can be born in the 20th century and die in the 19th.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.08,0:37:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And it's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.13,0:37:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是我带你来这里的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I brought you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.47,0:37:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.33,0:37:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是我自己要来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I wanted to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.95,0:37:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那我呢 我见过特洛伊城的衰败\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What about me? I saw the fall of Troy,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.17,0:37:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,见过第五次世界大战\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}World War Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.91,0:37:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,还推动了波士顿茶会\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I pushed boxes at the Boston Tea Party.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.13,0:37:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我却要死在地牢里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now I'm gonna die in a dungeon,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.93,0:37:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,还是在卡迪夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}in Cardiff!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.81,0:37:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不止是死\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And it's not just dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.57,0:37:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会成为他们中的一员\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We're gonna become one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.59,0:38:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们死也要战死 -好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We'll go down fighting, yeah? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.09,0:38:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一起战死 -好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Together? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.29,0:38:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常高兴遇见了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm so glad I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.23,0:38:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.48,0:38:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,博士 博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Doctor! Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.84,0:38:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,把火灭了 开大煤气\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Turn off the flame, turn up the gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.57,0:38:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,把房间充满煤气 赶快\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now fill the room! All of it, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.68,0:38:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么 -把它们都开大\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What are you doing? - Turn it all on!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.49,0:38:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,把房间充满煤气\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Flood the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.30,0:38:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,聪明 煤气\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Brilliant, gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.52,0:38:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么 我们打算改为被煤气呛死吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What, so we choke to death instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.11,0:38:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我想得对吗 博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Am I correct, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.19,0:38:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这些生物是气态的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}These creatures are gaseous.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.45,0:38:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,把房间充满煤气 能把它们拉离宿主\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Fill the room with gas. It'll draw them out of the host,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.79,0:38:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,被吸到外面 就像毒液被吸出伤口\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}suck them into the air, like poison from a wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.60,0:38:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.09,0:38:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.25,0:38:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望这个理论能被证实 最好快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I hope that this theory will be validated... soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.75,0:38:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,当然立即见效最好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}If not immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.38,0:38:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,煤气多得是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Plenty more.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.66,0:39:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,有效果了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}It's working!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.13,0:39:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,格温妮丝 送他们回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Gwyneth, send them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.11,0:39:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说谎了 他们不是天使\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They lied, they're not angels!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.77,0:39:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Liars?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.18,0:39:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,看看他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Look at them!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.85,0:39:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你的父母在天有灵 看到这场面\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}If your mother and father could look down and see this,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.23,0:39:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他们也会这样说\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}they'd tell you the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.80,0:39:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会给你力量 快送他们回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}They'd give you the strength. Now send them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.30,0:39:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法呼吸了 -查尔斯 带她出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Can't breathe. - Charles, get her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.85,0:39:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会离开她 -他们太强大了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm not leaving her. - They're too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.32,0:39:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还记得你看过的那个世界吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Remember that world you saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.72,0:39:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,洛斯的世界 那些人们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Rose's world? All those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.51,0:39:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你把他们送回裂口\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}None of it will exist
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.99,0:39:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不然他们都不会存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}unless you send them back through the rift!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.62,0:39:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法送他们回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I can't send them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.58,0:39:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但我能困住他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But I can hold them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.62,0:39:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,把他们约束在这里 这个房间里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Hold them in this place. Hold them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.92,0:39:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.52,0:39:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.56,0:39:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,离开这个房间\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.50,0:39:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,洛斯 出去 快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Rose, get out, go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.49,0:39:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定会救她脱险的 快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I won't leave her while she's still in danger. Now go!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.19,0:39:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 把它给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Come on. Leave that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.62,0:40:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这边走\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.06,0:40:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.08,0:40:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.23,0:40:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,她没能逃出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.46,0:40:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 她关闭了裂口\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I'm sorry. She closed the rift.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.65,0:41:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,付出了太大的代价\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}At such a cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.56,0:41:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可怜的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The poor child.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.17,0:41:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我努力过 洛斯 但格温妮丝早已死去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I did try, Rose, but Gwyneth was already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.13,0:41:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,她至少五分钟前就死去了 -什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She had been for at least five minutes. - What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.33,0:41:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为她站在拱门下方那一刻就已经死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I think she was dead from the minute she stood in that arch.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.51,0:41:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But she can't have,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.04,0:41:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,她对我们说话 帮助我们 还救了我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}she spoke to us, she helped us, she saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.19,0:41:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,她怎么能做到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How could she have done that?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.37,0:41:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,天堂和人世间的事物\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}There are more things in Heaven and Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.44,0:41:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要比你能想象的多得多\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}than are dreamt of in your philosophy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.54,0:41:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,即便对你也是 博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Even for you, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.96,0:41:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,她拯救了这个世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}She saved the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.79,0:41:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,一个女佣\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}A servant girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.44,0:41:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,却没人会知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And no-one will ever know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.73,0:41:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 小查理 我这就要回我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Right then, Charlie boy, I've just got to go into my, erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.06,0:41:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,小木屋了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.03,0:42:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不用很久\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Won't be long.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.69,0:42:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你接下来要怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.23,0:42:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我要坐邮车返回伦敦\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I shall take the mail-coach back to London,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.63,0:42:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,尽快回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}quite literally post-haste.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.56,0:42:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能再这般独自一人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This is no time for me to be on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.02,0:42:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我要与家人共度圣诞 弥补过失\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I shall spend Christmas with my family and make amends to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.69,0:42:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,见识过今晚的一切后\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}After all I've learnt tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.85,0:42:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了家人才是最重要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}there can be nothing more vital.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.83,0:42:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你振作起来了 -非常振作\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You've cheered up. - Exceedingly!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.21,0:42:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,早晨我还以为我通晓世间万物\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}This morning, I thought I knew everything in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.58,0:42:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在才知道那只是冰山一角\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Now I know I've just started.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.78,0:42:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那些宏大又绝妙的见解 博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}All these huge and wonderful notions, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.38,0:42:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我受到了启发 我一定要写写它们的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I am inspired, I must write about them!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.92,0:42:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为这样好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Do you think that's wise?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.32,0:42:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我会谨慎处理的 开始的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I shall be subtle, at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.61,0:42:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,《艾德温·德鲁德之谜》还缺个结局\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The Mystery Of Edwin Drood still lacks an ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.02,0:42:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,也许凶手不是男孩的叔叔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Perhaps the killer was not the boy's uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.27,0:42:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,也许凶手根本不属于这个世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Perhaps he was not of this earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.76,0:42:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,《艾德温·德鲁德之谜》和《蓝色元素》\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}The Mystery Of Edwin Drood And The Blue Elementals!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.97,0:42:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我要广为传播 揭示真相\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I can spread the word, tell the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.13,0:42:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那祝你好运了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Good luck with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.26,0:43:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你 太棒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Nice to meet you, fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.55,0:43:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那么再见 多谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Bye, then. And thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.15,0:43:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, my dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.36,0:43:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真新潮\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}How modern.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.77,0:43:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 但我不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Thank you. But I don't understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.09,0:43:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么告别呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}in what way is this goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.94,0:43:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要去哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.70,0:43:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你马上就知道了 我进去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You'll see. In the shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.55,0:43:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,发自内心地说 博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Upon my soul, Doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.75,0:43:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,和你一起真是谜题不断\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}it's one riddle after another with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.17,0:43:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但在揭露这些真相后\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But after all these revelations,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.29,0:43:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一个谜你没有解释\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}there's one mystery you still haven't explained.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.61,0:43:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Answer me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.35,0:43:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.27,0:43:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,只是一个路过的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Just a friend. Passing through.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.82,0:43:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但你对未来世界了解甚多\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But you have such knowledge of future times.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.91,0:43:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我不希望勉强你 但我想问你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}I don't wish to impose on you but I must ask you,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.57,0:43:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我写的书 博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}my books... Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.41,0:43:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,它们流传了吗 -当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Do they last? - Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.29,0:43:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,流传了多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}For how long?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.14,0:44:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,永远\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.60,0:44:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.90,0:44:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,小屋 进去吧 洛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Shed. Come on, Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.47,0:44:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 进这个盒子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What? In the box?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.44,0:44:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩都进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Both of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.69,0:44:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静 伙计\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Down, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.44,0:44:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,再会\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.51,0:44:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他写蓝色的鬼魂 不就改变历史了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Doesn't that change history, if he writes about blue ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.75,0:44:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,一个星期后就是1870年\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}In a week's time, it's 1870.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.57,0:44:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他的大限将至 很遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}And that's the year he dies. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.04,0:44:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他无法将这个故事讲给世人听了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}He'll never get to tell his story.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.46,0:44:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不 他这么好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Oh, no. He was so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.30,0:44:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但是在你的时代 他已经死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}But in your time, he was already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.95,0:44:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经使他复活了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}We've brought him back to life
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.64,0:44:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,比任何时候都生龙活虎 老查理\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}and he's more alive now than he's ever been. Old Charlie Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.23,0:44:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们给他最后一个惊喜\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Let's give him one last surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.19,0:45:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐 先生 -你也圣诞快乐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Merry Christmas, sir. - Merry Christmas to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.23,0:45:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝保佑我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}God bless us.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.32,0:45:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,保佑所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Every one.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.49,0:45:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,400)\pos(171.856,183.273)}{\fn黑体\fs28\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}下集预告
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.41,0:45:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn黑体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}飞碟坠落伦敦 大本钟被毁
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.08,0:45:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn黑体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}外星人应急响应及求助热线
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.52,0:45:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,一架飞碟坠落于伦敦中央导致大本钟被毁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Big Ben destroyed as a UFO crash lands in Central London.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.78,0:45:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你们已被逮捕 离开那个盒子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}You are now under arrest. Step away from that box.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.30,0:45:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,把手举过头顶 你们被捕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Raise your hands above your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.88,0:45:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢 它们是要入侵吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}What is it then? Are they invading?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.57,0:45:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,多有趣的入侵方法 把全世界的人都惊到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Funny way to invade, putting the world on red alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.97,0:45:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,如果必要 我甚至可以对全国实施军事管制\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}My God, I'll put this country under marshal law if I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.31,0:45:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,启用Δ防御计划 快 出动 出动\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Defence part Delta! Come on, move, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.09,0:45:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020&\shad0.6}Clear!
